# Settleora

Self-hosted cross-platform expense management, shared bill tracking, settlement workflow, receipt OCR, recurring bills, and forecasting.

## Repo structure
- `docs/` project requirements and architecture
- `apps/mobile/` Flutter mobile app
- `apps/web-user/` user web portal
- `apps/web-admin/` admin web portal
- `services/api/` backend API
- `services/worker-ocr/` OCR worker
- `infra/` deployment, Docker, environment, CI/CD support